Changes:
 ros-one-robot-calibration (0.7.2-3-g80c2be2-2024.12.24.21.33) jammy; urgency=high
 .
   * calibrate falling attributes as well if they exist (#144 <https://github.com/mikeferguson/robot_calibration/issues/144>)
